{"id":282755,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-上海等各省市维权人士在北京拉横幅抗议/","date":"2013-03-07T21:00:41Z","modified":"2013-03-07T21:00:41Z","title":"维权网 | 上海等各省市维权人士在北京拉横幅抗议腐败（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员雷鸣、疾风报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">42</span><span>分，来自上海的朱金娣、陈建芳、王永凤、周炎、韦开珍；广西的曾传贤；浙江的金丽丽；云南的王美兰；河南的刘志法等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>位上访维权人士，在北京的某处草地上，拉起写有“访民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8220;</span><span>非访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8220;</span><span>是腐败政府所逼”的横幅示威。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家认为，在中国许多公民都是遵纪守法的好公民。但是，由于地方政府为了自己的私利，与民争利，以权代法，司法不公，迫使老百姓走上维权之路。更有地方政府为了掩盖犯罪事实，当许多维权者走出国家信访大门时，就被地方政府带回当地拘留，劳教，甚至判刑。地方政府还利用信纺终结制度，不按法律法规化解矛盾。这样，信访事项听证会就变成骑在访民头上的霸王会。更有的信访人连听证会都没开过确，就莫名奇妙被终结，关闭了每个信访人的维权大门。国家信访局纵容地方政府的非法信访终结的行为，把维权信访人完全关在国家信访办大门外。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家表示：最近，最高法院下令不受理有关信访人，诉讼地方政府终结渎职侵权的行为等，逼得信访人走投无路，信访人只能找中央领导。如果找领导也算</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8220;</span><span>非访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8220;</span><span>，那都是腐败政府逼迫污陷的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fia1Eo_6Ido/UTiozt1WKzI/AAAAAAAAef0/gsndldjc8F4/s1600/DSCI0125.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fia1Eo_6Ido/UTiozt1WKzI/AAAAAAAAef0/gsndldjc8F4/s320/DSCI0125.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-33ypobrTfmU/UTio0i6BezI/AAAAAAAAef8/uhp2perC4js/s1600/DSCI0126.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-33ypobrTfmU/UTio0i6BezI/AAAAAAAAef8/uhp2perC4js/s320/DSCI0126.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eIMs5bK37bQ/UTio2VZovVI/AAAAAAAAegE/FOrmFvXfvyk/s1600/DSCI0127.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"308\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eIMs5bK37bQ/UTio2VZovVI/AAAAAAAAegE/FOrmFvXfvyk/s320/DSCI0127.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}